Computational Semantic Literature Analysis Pipeline for Cellulose Nanofiber Research
Version 1.0.2 (2026)

Copyright (C) 2026 Alfredo Enrique Villadiego del Villar

This repository contains the computational workflow developed for the
systematic literature review, semantic mapping, topic modeling, sentiment
analysis, and methodological rigor assessment of scientific literature on
cellulose nanofibers (CNFs).

The software retrieves bibliographic records directly from a Zotero library
through the Zotero Web API and performs Natural Language Processing (NLP),
semantic embedding generation, topic modeling (BERTopic), dimensionality
reduction (UMAP), density-based clustering (HDBSCAN), sentiment analysis,
bibliometric analysis, and publication-ready visualization.

